\mathbf{\Delta}x^n=(x+1)^n-x^n=\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}\binom{n}kx^k
\begin{align*} \mathbf{\Delta}^nx^n&=\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}\binom{n}k\mathbf{\Delta}^{n-1}x^k\\ &=\binom{n}{n-1}(n-1)!\\\\ &=n(n-1)!\\\\ &=n!\;, \end{align*}
