n!
 \sum_{k=0}^n (-1)^k {n\choose k}(x+n-k)^n 
D = \partial/\partial x
\begin{eqnarray*} \sum_{k=0}^{n}(-1)^{k}\binom{n}{k}(n-k+r)^{n} &=&  \sum_{k=0}^{n}(-1)^{n-k} \binom{n}{k}(k+r)^{n} \\ &=& \left.\left(x D\right)^n  \sum_{k=0}^{n} (-1)^{n-k} \binom{n}{k} x^{k+r}\right|_{x=1} \\ &=& \left.\left(x D\right)^n x^r(x-1)^n \right|_{x=1} \\ &=& \left.D^n (x-1)^n\right|_{x=1} \\ &=& n! \end{eqnarray*}
